data.description: This beautiful brick 3 Bedroom 2 Bath home is  country living with the convenience of being close to town. Sitting on a half acre is ready for its new family! Spacious kitchen, formal living and dining room, den with a beautiful rock fireplace and wood mantle complete with new laminate flooring. Large laundry room and a sunroom to enjoy the beautiful view in the back yard.  Detached shop built 2 years ago. Minutes from Robert Trent Jones.   Call today for your private showing! Buyer to verify all info.
